      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1767920788408,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Plan A: The server dictates how the things move on the screen.\n            The clients only send the commands.\n- Plan B: The player move freely and everything else move based\n            on what we receive from server.\nObs: Don't matter the apprach the use of linear interpolation (LERP)\n      based on the client's latency against the server. A threshold\n      should be implemented to preserve the gameplay's quality.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Plan A: The server dictates how the things move on the screen.\n            The clients only send the commands.\n- Plan B: The player move freely and everything else move based\n            on what we receive from server.\nObs: Don't matter the apprach the use of linear interpolation (LERP)\n      based on the client's latency against the server. A threshold\n      should be implemented to preserve the gameplay's quality.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
